  <script>_satellite["_runScript1"](function(event, target, Promise) {

function waitNoneYalo(selector) {

  return new Promise((resolve) => {

    if (document.querySelector(selector)) {

      return resolve(document.querySelector(selector));

    }



    const observer = new MutationObserver(() => {

      if (document.querySelector(selector)) {

        resolve(document.querySelector(selector));

        observer.disconnect();

      }

    });



    observer.observe(document.body, {

      subtree: true,

      childList: true,

    });

  });

}



waitNoneYalo("#yalochat_button").then((element) => {

  element.style.display = "none";

  

});



(function () {

  let js = document.createElement("script");

  js.type = "text/javascript";

  js.async = 1;

  js.src = "https://go.botmaker.com/rest/webchat/p/I7FV7ODLIZ/init.js";

  document.body.appendChild(js);

})();



function waitSetWhatsaapBotmaker(selector) {

  return new Promise((resolve) => {

    if (document.querySelector(selector)) {

      return resolve(document.querySelector(selector));

    }



    const observer = new MutationObserver(() => {

      if (document.querySelector(selector)) {

        resolve(document.querySelector(selector));

        observer.disconnect();

      }

    });



    observer.observe(document.body, {

      subtree: true,

      childList: true,

    });

  });

}



waitSetWhatsaapBotmaker('[title="WhatsApp"]').then((element) => {

  let url_bm = window.location.href;

  let href = element.getAttribute("href");

  let image = document.querySelector('[title="WhatsApp"] > img');

  let toolTip = document.querySelector('[title="WhatsApp"] > div');

  element.setAttribute("href", href + url_bm);

  if (window.innerWidth < 960) {

    toolTip.style.display = "none";

    toolTip.style.bottom = "68px";

    toolTip.style.right = "65px";

    image.style.bottom = "70px";

    image.style.zIndex = "0";

  }

  

});





});</script>

function crearBadge(dispositivo,ubicacion){

    var price = document.getElementsByClassName(ubicacion)[0];

    var badge = document.createElement('img');

    badge.className = 'badge3D_RA'+dispositivo;

    badge.src = 'https://images.contentstack.io/v3/assets/blt2f8082df109cfbfb/blt3963332baea04c59/63ab4eecc4bb1011c9ca60d5/Bagde_3D_y_RA.svg ';

    if (dispositivo === 'M')

        price.before(badge);

    else

        price.append(badge);

}

function textoExperiencia(dispositivo,cltexto){

    var br = document.createElement('br');

    var p = document.createElement('p');

    p.className = 'experienceText2'+dispositivo;

    p.textContent = 'Visualiza, mide y compara aquí:';

    var experienceTxt = document.createElement('span');

    experienceTxt.className = cltexto;

    experienceTxt.textContent = 'Interactúa con tu producto:';

    p.prepend(experienceTxt,br);

    return p

}

function crearContenedorBotones(dispositivo){

    var buttons = document.createElement('div');

    buttons.className = 'buttonsRA_3D'+dispositivo;

    buttons.id='buttonsRA_3D'+dispositivo;

    return buttons

}

function crearBoton(dispositivo,tipo,url){

    var boton = document.createElement('button');

    boton.className = 'btn'+tipo+dispositivo;

    boton.id='btn'+tipo+dispositivo;

    var img = document.createElement('img');

    img.className = 'img'+tipo+dispositivo;

    img.id = 'img'+tipo+dispositivo;

    img.src = url;

    var text = document.createElement('span');

    text.className = 'text'+tipo+dispositivo;

    text.id = 'text'+tipo+dispositivo;

    text.innerHTML='Ver en '+(tipo==='RA'? 'mi espacio':'3D');

    boton.append(img,text);

    return boton;

}

function addtooTipMudi(dispositivo){

        setTimeout(()=>{

            const p = document.createElement('P');

            p.id='tooltipMudi'+dispositivo;

            p.innerHTML=` <span id="resaltarTooltip">¡Nuevo!</span> Prueba como se ve este producto en tu espacio usando las funciones de Realidad Aumentada y 3D`;

            const container = document.getElementById('buttonsRA_3D'+dispositivo);

            container.appendChild(p)},3000);

          setTimeout(()=>{

                    document.getElementById('tooltipMudi'+dispositivo).remove()},60000)

}

function crearModal(dispositivo,contenido){

    var clase_cuerpo_modal='bodyModal'+dispositivo;

    var contenedorModal = document.createElement('div');

    contenedorModal.className = 'modalMudi';

    contenedorModal.innerHTML ='<div class="'+clase_cuerpo_modal+'">'+contenido+'</div>';

    document.body.prepend(contenedorModal);

}

function cerrarModal(){

    var modal = document.getElementsByClassName('modalMudi')[0];

    modal.remove();

}

</script>

  function marcarWhatsapp() {

      var width = screen.width;

      var device = '';

      if (width > 767) {

          device = 'Desktop';

      } else { 

          device = 'Mobile';

      }

      var url = document.URL;

      gtag('event', device, { 'event_category': 'Click botón Whatsapp', 'event_label': url, 'value': ''});

  }

    function createNode(node) {

        newNode.className = "ContainerIndexed";

        newNode.innerHTML = '<div id="contenidoIndexado">';

        var newScript = document.createElement("script");

        newScript.type = "text/javascript";

        newScript.src = "https://storage.googleapis.com/indexado/assets/alquimioIndexado.v2.js";

        newNode.appendChild(newScript);

        newScript.dataset.sku = node;

        console.log(newNode);

        referenceNode.parentNode.insertBefore(newNode, referenceNode.nextSibling);

    }

  function insertAfter(referenceNode, newNode) {

      referenceNode.parentNode.insertBefore(newNode, referenceNode.nextSibling);

  }



  function insertBefore(referenceNode, newNode) {

      referenceNode.parentNode.insertBefore(newNode, referenceNode);

  }



  function detectOS() {

      var platform = navigator.platform.toLowerCase(),

          iosPlatforms = ['iphone', 'ipad', 'ipod', 'ipod touch'];



      if (platform.includes('mac')) return ('MacOS');

      if (iosPlatforms.includes(platform)) return ('iOS');

      if (platform.includes('win')) return ('Windows');

      if (/android/.test(navigator.userAgent.toLowerCase())) return ('Android');

      if (/linux/.test(platform)) return ('Linux');

  }



  (function() {



      var isRelAR = false;



      var a = document.createElement('a');



      if (a.relList.supports('ar')) {



          isRelAR = true;



      }



      document.documentElement.classList.add(isRelAR ? 'relar' : 'no-relar');



  })();

  //Cerrar Sticky QR

  function closeSticky() {

      var width = screen.width;

      if (width > 767) {

          var divS1 = document.getElementsByClassName('stycky-mudi')[0];

          divS1.style.display = 'none';

      }

      if (width < 768) {

          var divSM1 = document.getElementsByClassName('stycky-mudi')[0];

          divSM1.style.display = 'none';

      }

  }



  // iFrame manipulable

  function manipulateIframe(sku) {

      var divf1 = document.createElement("div");

      divf1.className = 'div3D';

      var iframe1 = document.createElement("iframe");

      iframe1.className = 'iframe3D';

      iframe1.src = 'https://viewer.mudi.com.co/v1/web?id=' + id + '&sku=' + sku;

      var width = screen.width;

      

      divf1.appendChild(iframe1);

      divf1.style.display = 'none';



      var canva = document.getElementsByClassName('product-image-wrapper')[0];

      var canvaMobile = document.getElementsByClassName('product-image-mobile')[0];



      var labelB1 = document.getElementsByClassName('ra-3d-mudi')[0];

      var picture = document.getElementsByClassName('product-image')[0];

      var pictureM = document.getElementById('s7viewer');

      var d3d = document.getElementsByClassName('div3D')[0];

              

      if (width > 767) {

          if (canva.style.display != 'none') {

              insertBefore(canva, divf1);

              canva.style.display = 'none';

              divf1.style.display = 'flex';

              labelB1.style.padding = '10px 0px 0px 20px';

              divf1.appendChild(labelB1);

              marcarAnalytics('3D');

          } else {

              canva.style.display = 'flex';

              //d3d.style.display = 'none';

              d3d.remove();

              picture.appendChild(labelB1);

              labelB1.style.padding = '0px';

          }

      } else {



          if (canvaMobile.style.display != 'none') {

              insertBefore(canvaMobile, divf1);

              canvaMobile.style.display = 'none';

              divf1.style.display = 'flex';

              divf1.appendChild(labelB1);

              marcarAnalytics('3D');

          } else {

              canvaMobile.style.display = 'block';

              //divf1.style.display = 'none';

              d3d.remove();

              pictureM.appendChild(labelB1);

          }

      }

  }



  function insertAfter(referenceNode, newNode) {

      referenceNode.parentNode.insertBefore(newNode, referenceNode.nextSibling);

  }



  function insertBefore(referenceNode, newNode) {

      referenceNode.parentNode.insertBefore(newNode, referenceNode);

  }



  //Detectar sistema operativo

  function detectOS() {

      var platform = navigator.platform.toLowerCase(),

          iosPlatforms = ['iphone', 'ipad', 'ipod', 'ipod touch'];



      if (platform.includes('mac')) return ('MacOS');

      if (iosPlatforms.includes(platform)) return ('iOS');

      if (platform.includes('win')) return ('Windows');

      if (/android/.test(navigator.userAgent.toLowerCase())) return ('Android');

      if (/linux/.test(platform)) return ('Linux');

  }



  (function() {



      var isRelAR = false;



      var a = document.createElement('a');



      if (a.relList.supports('ar')) {



          isRelAR = true;



      }



      document.documentElement.classList.add(isRelAR ? 'relar' : 'no-relar');



  })();



  function marcarAnalytics(selectedButton) {

    var selctdButton = 'click botón ' + selectedButton + ' Mudi';

    product = digitalData.ecom.sku;

    var width = screen.width;

    var device = '';

    if (width > 767) {

        device = 'Desktop_Mudi';

    } else { 

        device = 'Mobile_Mudi';

    }

    var url = document.URL;

    gtag('event', selctdButton, { 'event_category': device, 'event_label': product, 'value': ''});

    console.log('evento marcado');

  }

		function showPopUp() {

		    div2.style.display = 'block';

		    step1.style.display = 'block';

		    document.getElementById("closebtn").addEventListener("click", closeModal);

		var step2 = document.getElementsByClassName("paso-02")[0];

		var step3 = document.getElementsByClassName("paso-03")[0];

		var step4 = document.getElementsByClassName("paso-04")[0];

		var step5 = document.getElementsByClassName("paso-05")[0];

		var step6 = document.getElementsByClassName("paso-06")[0];

		

		function showNextStep() {

		    if (step1.style.display == 'block') {

		        step1.style.display = 'none';

		        step2.style.display = 'block';

		    } else if (step2.style.display == 'block') {

		        step2.style.display = 'none';

		        step3.style.display = 'block';

		    } else if (step3.style.display == 'block') {

		        step3.style.display = 'none';

		        step4.style.display = 'block';

		    } else if (step4.style.display == 'block') {

		        step4.style.display = 'none';

		        step5.style.display = 'block';

		    } else if (step5.style.display == 'block') {

		        step5.style.display = 'none';

		        step6.style.display = 'block';

		    } else if (step6.style.display == 'block') {

		        step6.style.display = 'none';

		        div2.style.display = 'none';

		    }

		

		}

		

		function showLastStep() {

		    if (step1.style.display == 'block') {

		        div2.style.display = 'none';

		        step1.style.display = 'none';

		    } else if (step2.style.display == 'block') {

		        step1.style.display = 'block';

		        step2.style.display = 'none';

		    } else if (step3.style.display == 'block') {

		        step2.style.display = 'block';

		        step3.style.display = 'none';

		    } else if (step4.style.display == 'block') {

		        step3.style.display = 'block';

		        step4.style.display = 'none';

		    } else if (step5.style.display == 'block') {

		        step4.style.display = 'block';

		        step5.style.display = 'none';

		    } else if (step6.style.display == 'block') {

		        step5.style.display = 'block';

		        step6.style.display = 'none';

		    }

		

		}

		

		function closeModal() {

		    div2.style.display = 'none';

		    step1.style.display = 'none';

		    step2.style.display = 'none';

		    step3.style.display = 'none';

		    step4.style.display = 'none';

		    step5.style.display = 'none';

		    step6.style.display = 'none';

		}

		

		function insertAfter(newNode, referenceNode) {

		    referenceNode.parentNode.insertBefore(newNode, referenceNode.nextSibling);

		}

		

	}

  

</script>
